content:
You can now send non-marketing emails to opted-out prospects directly from Engagement Studio.

Transfer your images to a Salesforce CMS workspace where they can be accessed for future marketing initiatives.

Access alerts and feature recommendation banners in a dedicated messaging section within the Account Engagement Optimizer.

Access more of your data with new updates for version 5 of Account Engagement API.

The Engage for Gmail Chrome extension, built on Manifest V2, is projected to retire in June 2024. You can continue to send emails directly through Salesforce using the Account Engagement Sales Email & Alerts feature.
title: Marketing Cloud Account Engagement Updates
